@NODE Mod_Internal_Normal "Normal"
@TOC Listview

	SwazBlanker/Internal Blanker : Normal
	=====================================

	This is probably the most effective screen blanker method to date. It
	makes the screen go blank, which is after-all what a screen blanker is
	supposed to do.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Mod_Internal_Random "Random"
@TOC Listview

	SwazBlanker/Internal Blanker : Random
	=====================================

	This picks a disk based blanker at random from the @{" listview " LINK ListView}.
	Only ticked blankers can be chosen for the blanker, they are also
	chosen without replacement so you can have a different blanker each
	time.

	If no blankers are ticked then the @{" Normal " LINK Mod_Internal_Normal} blanker will be used.

@ENDNODE

